<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="description" content="site to book hotel" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Details</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/views/detailspagestyle.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="/index.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="content">
    {{> header}}
    <div class="main">
      <div class="img-container">
        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
          </ol>
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
              <img class="d-block w-100" src="/{{details.fileName}}" width="auto" height="500px" alt="First slide"
                style="position: relative" />
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img class="d-block w-100" src="/pictures/photo1-1.jpg" width="auto" height="auto" alt="Second slide"
                style="position: relative" />
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img class="d-block w-100" src="/pictures/photo1-2.jpg" width="auto" height="auto" alt="Third slide"
                style="position: relative" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
          </a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="descr">
        <h1>{{details.title}}</h1>
        <p>
          {{details.desc}}
        </p>
        <p>Place for two</p>
        <p>Price: ${{details.price}} CAD/night</p>
        <div class="book">
          <form action="/confirmation/{{details._id}}" method="POST">
            <label for="in">Check-In</label>
            <input type="date" id="in" name="in" required>
            <label for="out">Check-Out</label>
            <input type="date" id="out" name="out" required>
            <input type="submit" class="button" value="Book Now">
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="comments">
        <h1>Rating</h1>
        <p>
          Aenean convallis condimentum scelerisque. Praesent nec commodo dui.
          Duis dapibus, augue vitae dictum aliquam, sapien tellus mollis sem,
          ac aliquet erat purus et velit. Sed tristique velit eget ipsum
          fringilla porta. Donec in lorem et metus fermentum maximus sit amet
          id ipsum. Aenean porttitor ultrices facilisis. Sed convallis ante id
          nibh sodales vehicula. Cras in est lacinia, tristique ipsum vel,
          euismod nisl. Nam vitae turpis dui. Proin et lorem arcu. Duis
          suscipit, justo et imperdiet posuere, quam ligula gravida nunc, quis
          finibus nibh nisl ac enim. Vestibulum condimentum neque magna, vel
          fringilla metus luctus id. Nam quam leo, bibendum a lacinia vitae,
          posuere eget diam. Aliquam varius urna pulvinar risus dictum rutrum
          vel ut nibh.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
        <div class="h">
          <h1>Services</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="breakfast">
          <img src="/pictures/breakfast2.svg" alt="breakfast" width="35px" height="35px">
          <p>Breakfast</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tv">
          <img src="/pictures/tv.svg" alt="tv" width="35px" height="35px">
          <p>Television</p>
        </div>
        <div class="wifi">
          <img src="/pictures/wifi.svg" alt="wifi" width="35px" height="35px">
          <p>Wi-Fi</p>
        </div>
        <div class="washer">
          <img src="/pictures/washer.svg" alt="washer" width="35px" height="35px">
          <p>Washer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="dryer">
          <img src="/pictures/hair-dryer.svg" alt="dryer" width="35px" height="35px">
          <p>Hair Dryer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ac">
          <img src="/pictures/air-conditioning.svg" alt="ac" width="35px" height="35px">
          <p>Air conditioning</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{> footer}}
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>